  <section id="about" class="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>I'm a Business Management major at California State University, Northridge, also completing some courses at Los Angeles Pierce College. About halfway through my degree, on track to graduate in four years.</p>
    <p>Outside the classroom, I serve as Rush Chair for AEPi and in the past was the Vice President of CSUN's Interfraternity Council — work that's taught me more about people, logistics, and persuasion than any lecture has.</p>
    <div class="roles">
      <span>Rush Chair, AEPi</span>
      <span>VP, CSUN IFC</span>
      <span>Business Management · CSUN</span>
    </div>
